io.sphere.sdk.categories

Interface Category

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CreationTimestamped, DefaultModel<Category>, DefaultModelView<Category>, Identifiable<Category>, MetaAttributes, Referenceable<Category>, Timestamped, Versioned<Category>, WithLocalizedSlug
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CategoryWrapper

    public interface Category
extends DefaultModel<Category>, WithLocalizedSlug, MetaAttributes
    Categories are used to organize products in a hierarchical structure.

    Operations:

    • Create a category with CategoryCreateCommand.
    • Create a category test double with CategoryBuilder.
    • Update a category with CategoryUpdateCommand.
    • Delete a category with CategoryDeleteCommand.
